		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I just watched the AVGN episode of action 52 and i was wondering if somebody here ever looked at the games programming errors?
<br />
<br />Looking for action 52 on the forum gave a couple of topics about the sound.
<br />And i must say that the sound is pretty good.(intro)
<br />
<br />But the games have some programming errors like : jumping/control problems,dying in mid air,etc.etc.
<br />
<br />Might be ''FUN'' to look at .

		

		</td>
