		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The game could probably be hacked to some sort of GNROM-on-steroids mapper, but the PRG ROM is three times the size of the biggest PRG ROM that the PowerPak supports. The games would need to somehow share much of their code. How much of the code is unique to each game and how much is copypasta?

		

		</td>
