		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />We'd might as well just make our own Action 52 at that rate. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" />
<br />
<br />A lot of the games seem to be very similar to The Games Factory and Klik N Play. That is, a basic game framework that supports a couple of different movement types (such as 8-directional, gravity-based, etc), but with the same system for actors and music, which is common to all games.
<br />
<br />hah, we'd probably be able to store the finished product in less space than the original, too. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" />

		

